'''Nkllonian lava extract''' was an illegal drug at the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Extracted from the metal [[xonolite]] consumed by [[Mustafar/Legends|Mustafar's]] [[Jawenko lava beast]], the drug was often transported to [[Nkllon/Legends|Nkllon]], where it became an underworld craze.<ref name="UA">{{Hyperspace|url=hyperspace/member/insideronline/89/indexp3.html|text=Underworld Appendix: Swoops, Spice, and Wretched Rogues|int=Underworld Appendix: Swoops, Spice, and Wretched Rogues}}</ref>

When taken, the Nkllonian lava extract entered the user's bloodstream and liquefied their internal organs. If one used one hundred percent of it at once, they would spontaneously combust. This deadly side effect was famously revealed when it happened to a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Balosar (species)/Legends|Balosar]] from [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="UA" />

